# Sweet Shop Management System

## Project Overview
The **Sweet Shop Management System** is a modern web application designed to manage a sweet shop's operations efficiently. It allows users to register, log in, browse sweets, and make purchases. Admins can manage sweets inventory and track sales.

**Technologies Used:**
- Frontend: React.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Spring Boot (Java), Spring Security, Spring Data JPA
- Database: MySQL
- Dev Tools: Maven, Git, Postman
- AI Assistance: ChatGPT, GitHub Copilot

---

## Features

### User Features
- User Registration and Login
- Browse All Available Sweets
- Search and Filter Sweets
- Purchase Sweets (with quantity validation)
- View Purchase History

### Admin Features
- Add, Update, Delete Sweets
- View Sweets Inventory
- Track Purchases and Sales
- Role-Based Access Control

---

## Project Structure

sweetshop-frontend-2
├─ src/
│ ├─ components/
│ │ ├─ Login.tsx
│ │ ├─ Register.tsx
│ │ ├─ Dashboard.tsx
│ ├─ contexts/
│ │ └─ AuthContext.tsx
│ ├─ services/
│ │ └─ api.ts
│ └─ App.tsx
└─ package.json
sweetshop-backend
├─ src/main/java/com/project/SweetShopManagement/
│ ├─ controller/
│ ├─ model/
│ ├─ repository/
│ └─ service/
├─ pom.xml

