## Installation & Setup

### Backend
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/sweetshop-management.git
Navigate to backend folder:

bash
Copy code
cd sweetshop-backend
Update application.properties with your MySQL credentials.

Build and run the Spring Boot app:

bash
Copy code
mvn clean install
mvn spring-boot:run
Frontend
Navigate to frontend folder:

bash
Copy code
cd sweetshop-frontend-2
Install dependencies:

bash
Copy code
npm install
Start the React development server:

bash
Copy code
npm start
API Endpoints
Method	Endpoint	Description
POST	/api/auth/register	Register a new user
POST	/api/auth/login	Login user and get JWT token
GET	/api/sweets	Fetch all sweets
POST	/api/sweets	Add a new sweet (Admin only)
PUT	/api/sweets/:id	Update sweet details (Admin only)
DELETE	/api/sweets/:id	Delete sweet (Admin only)
POST	/api/purchase	Purchase sweet (User)

My AI Usage
During the development of this project, I used AI tools to enhance productivity, brainstorm ideas, and generate code snippets.

Tools Used
ChatGPT: Assisted in writing React components, generating backend service logic, and debugging errors.

GitHub Copilot: Suggested code completions, generated unit tests, and helped scaffold functions for API integration.

How AI Was Used
Frontend Development:

Used ChatGPT to generate the Login and Register components with proper error handling and loading states.

Copilot helped autocomplete repetitive JSX code, form validations, and Tailwind CSS classes.

Backend Development:

ChatGPT suggested Spring Boot controller and service methods for managing sweets and purchases.

Copilot generated repository methods and DTO mappings.

Debugging & Optimization:

ChatGPT helped identify and solve Babel parsing errors in the frontend.

Suggested TypeScript typings and proper API response handling.

Reflection on AI Impact
AI significantly improved my workflow by:

Reducing repetitive coding tasks.

Offering multiple ways to structure code and handle edge cases.

Helping quickly troubleshoot errors, saving hours of debugging.

Boosting confidence in implementing TypeScript + React + Spring Boot integration.
Overall, AI acted as a virtual pair programmer, enhancing productivity and code quality.

